{"tid":1797818,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［樂文文具道歉聲明］手足！對不起！我們真的錯了！","createTime":"2019-12-25T17:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T05:23:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd239911c6b25d4285b8abf215f924055ad7f4a5","tid":1797818,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"［樂文文具道歉聲明］<br />\n<br />\n手足！對不起！我們真的錯了！<br />\n<br />\n有關於 Pepe the Frog Hong Kong 事宜，自6月運動以來，小編及本店都是手足既陣營，亦明白今次事件中得到既資訊的確有誤，而搞到滿城風雨，而且令到好多手足受到傷害，真的對不起！<br />\n<br />\n每天小編要處理業務，小朋友等問題。現在我們清楚知道真相，賣Pepe的也絕不是人血饅頭，並與香港人並肩作戰！<br />\n<br />\n在此小編謹在此向各位手足及受影響人士致歉！<br />\n<br />\n亦多謝身邊朋友向我們解說手上資訊的問題所在，我們仍然善意歡迎所有手足意見，希望各位也仍然是一樣對準「暴政」！<br />\n<br />\n最後謹祝大家聖誕平安！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n#PEPE都是大家的<br />\n#樂文文具 #要從錯誤中成長<br />\n#香港人加油<br />\n#還要走很長的路<br />\n#明的會明不解釋<br />\n#攰了休息後再行<br />\n#bewater<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/561818047329183/posts/1516776855166626/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F561818047329183%2Fposts%2F1516776855166626%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFGiIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=4fa27555\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/561818047329183/posts/1516776855166626/</a>"},{"pid":"64ef1acd793906f6bae4bf51fa8ab5752402b244","tid":1797818,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:20:29.000Z","msg":"連始作俑者樂文都肯道歉<br />\n<br />\n連登仔肯道歉未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b620a9ecdc470cb4d8f79eedd57b63036f3a4d","tid":1797818,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f5c7e0da8ac881ac134e1fa962a3a421e9714dc","tid":1797818,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/moc